  toggle, course image upload, and all core course fields. The Content,
  Options, and Quiz tabs are shells at this stage — filled in Phases 4, 5, 6.

HOW IT WORKS IN THE SYSTEM:
  - GET  /api/v1/courses/:id returns course detail
  - PUT  /api/v1/courses/:id updates course fields
  - PATCH /api/v1/courses/:id/publish toggles is_published
  - Header: Publish toggle, Preview button, Add Attendees, Contact Attendees
  - Tabs persist active state in URL query param (?tab=content)
  - Auto-save on blur for text fields (optional) or Save button

