# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PHASE 5 — Quiz Builder (Instructor)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
STATUS: [ ] Pending
COMPLETED_DATE: —

WHAT THIS PHASE DOES:
  Builds the Quiz tab and the full quiz builder page. Instructors create
  quizzes, add questions with multiple options, mark correct answers, and
  configure attempt-based point rewards.

HOW IT WORKS IN THE SYSTEM:
  - Quizzes are linked to a course (course_id)
  - Each quiz has: title, questions[], reward_config (4 attempt tiers)
  - Each question has: text, options[], correct_option_ids[]
  - Reward config: { attempt_1_pts, attempt_2_pts, attempt_3_pts, attempt_4plus_pts }
  - Quiz builder is a full page (not a modal) for sufficient space
  - Left panel: question list + Add Question + Rewards buttons
  - Right panel: question editor

DATABASE TABLES CREATED:
  quizzes (id, course_id FK, title, attempt_1_points, attempt_2_points,
           attempt_3_points, attempt_4plus_points, created_at, updated_at)
  questions (id, quiz_id FK, text, sort_order, created_at, updated_at)
  question_options (id, question_id FK, text, is_correct, sort_order)

